#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:2
msgid "ROS2接口使用说明"
msgstr "ROS2 Interface Instructions"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:8
msgid "概述"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:9
msgid ""
"控制器采用的系统是Ubuntu22.04LTS，对应的ROS2版本是Humble。机械臂ROS2相关接口是基于ros2 "
"control框架构建的，因此使用ROS2控制的时候，需要特别留意版本对齐，以免出现DDS通讯版本不兼容的情况。"
msgstr ""
"The system used by the controller is Ubuntu 22.04 LTS, corresponding to ROS2"
" version Humble. The mechanical arm ROS2 related interfaces are built based "
"on the ros2 control framework. Therefore, when using ROS2 control, special "
"attention should be paid to version alignment to avoid DDS communication "
"version incompatibility issues."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:12
msgid "ros2 conrol插件的启动"
msgstr "Start of ros2 control plugin"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:13
msgid ""
"首先，需要使用SSH登录控制器，控制器上的LAN1口设定ip为”192.168.58.1”，LAN2口设定ip为”192.168.137.77”。需要将上位机设定到对应网段的不同ip，才可以使用SSH登录。"
msgstr ""
"First, use SSH to log in to the controller. Set the IP of LAN1 port on the "
"controller to \"192.168.58.1\" and the IP of LAN2 port to "
"\"192.168.137.77\". The host computer needs to be set to a different IP in "
"the corresponding subnet in order to use SSH login."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:15
msgid ""
"我们假设使用Tera "
"term软件登录SSH，打开软件，得到如下界面，再主机框中输入对应口的ip，我们假设使用LAN1口，因此ip应该填写192.168.58.1。"
msgstr ""
"We assume using Tera Term software to log in via SSH, open the software, and"
" get the following interface. Enter the IP address corresponding to the port"
" in the Host field. We assume using the LAN1 port, so the IP should be "
"filled as 192.168.58.1."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "038.png"
msgstr "038.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:22
msgid "图表 5-1 Tera term初始界面"
msgstr "Figure 5-1 Tera Term Initial Interface"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:23
msgid "点击确定后，会弹出提示框，输入用户名fairino，密码1，然后点击确定。"
msgstr ""
"After clicking OK, a prompt box will appear. Enter the username \"fairino\" "
"and password \"1\", then click OK."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "039.png"
msgstr "039.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:30
msgid "图表 5-2 登录界面"
msgstr "Figure 5-2 Login Interface"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:31
msgid ""
"进入bash界面之后，如果是单臂用户，使用cd指令进入single_ART3_R7_project文件夹，若是双臂用户，进入dual_ART3_R7_project。"
msgstr ""
"After entering the bash interface, if it is a single-arm user, use the cd "
"command to enter the single_ART3_R7_project folder, and if it is a dual-arm "
"user, enter the dual_ART3_R7_project."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "040.png"
msgstr "040.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:38
msgid "图表 5-3 进入单臂工程文件夹"
msgstr "Figure 5-3 Enter the Single-arm Engineering Folder"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:39
msgid "输入./runqhal.sh指令，启动底层HAL库程序，建立机械臂通讯，此时会提示输入密码，输入1然后回车即可。"
msgstr ""
"Enter the command ./runqhal.sh to start the underlying HAL library program "
"and establish communication with the robotic arm. At this point, you will be"
" prompted to enter a password. Enter 1 and press Enter."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "041.png"
msgstr "041.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:46
msgid "图表 5-4 启动HAL库程序"
msgstr "Figure 5-4 Starting the HAL Library Program"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:47
msgid "等待10s之后，再输入./runplguin指令，即可启动ros2 control插件程序，等待约10s，手臂可以进入使能状态。"
msgstr ""
"After waiting 10s, enter the command ./runplguin to start the ros2 control "
"plugin program. Wait about 10s, the arm can enter the enabled state."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "042.png"
msgstr "042.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:54
msgid "图表 5-5 启动ros2 control插件程序"
msgstr "Figure 5-5 Launch ros2 control Plugin Program"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:56
msgid "ros2 control接口说明"
msgstr "ROS2 Control Interface Documentation"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:57
msgid ""
"单臂下的配置参考下图所示，插件会启动一个名为single_arm_controller的控制器，类型是joint_trajectory_controller/JointTrajectoryController。另外，插件还会启动joint_state_broadcaster这个控制器，类型是joint_state_broadcaster/JointStateBroadcaster。"
msgstr ""
"The configuration under a single arm is shown in the figure below. The "
"plugin will start a controller named single_arm_controller, which is of type"
" joint_trajectory_controller/JointTrajectoryController. Additionally, the "
"plugin will also start the controller named joint_state_broadcaster, which "
"is of type joint_state_broadcaster/JointStateBroadcaster."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "043.png"
msgstr "043.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:64
msgid "图表 5-6 单臂配置参考"
msgstr "Figure 5-6 Single-arm Configuration Reference"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:65
msgid ""
"双臂下的配置参考下图所示，插件会启动一个名为dual_arm_controller的控制器，类型是joint_trajectory_controller/JointTrajectoryController。Joint_state_bradcaster这个控制器也会启动启动。"
msgstr ""
"The configuration under the arms is referenced in the figure below. The "
"plugin will start a controller named dual_arm_controller, of type "
"joint_trajectory_controller/JointTrajectoryController. The controller "
"joint_state_bradcaster will also be started."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "044.png"
msgstr "044.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:72
msgid "图表 5-7 双臂配置参考"
msgstr "Figure 5-7 Dual-arm Configuration Reference"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:74
msgid "远程桌面的使用"
msgstr "Using Remote Desktop"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:75
msgid ""
"控制器中集成了xrdp远程桌面，方便习惯使用图形化界面的用户拷贝文件，编写代码等操作，注意：远程桌面的用户权限无法让ros2 "
"control插件获取实时优先级，因此启动HAL程序和ros2 control插件务必注意不能在远程桌面中进行。 "
"假设使用windows系统登录远程桌面，打开windows的远程桌面服务，在文本框中输入ip地址，假设连接的是LAN1口，那么ip地址应该是192.168.58.1。"
msgstr ""
"The controller integrates xrdp remote desktop, which is convenient for users"
" who are accustomed to using a graphical interface to copy files, write "
"code, etc. Note: the user permissions of the remote desktop cannot allow the"
" ros2 control plugin to obtain real-time priority. Therefore, when starting "
"the HAL program and the ros2 control plugin, be sure not to perform these "
"operations in the remote desktop. Assuming you are using the Windows system "
"to log in to the remote desktop, open the Windows remote desktop service, "
"and enter the IP address in the text box. If the connection is via the LAN1 "
"port, the IP address should be 192.168.58.1."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "045.png"
msgstr "045.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:83
msgid "图表 5-8 远程桌面连接"
msgstr "Figure 5-8 Remote Desktop Connection"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:84
msgid "点击连接后，跳出xrdp登录界面，username输入fairino，password是1，然后点击ok。"
msgstr ""
"After clicking the link, the xrdp login interface pops up. Enter username as"
" fairino and password as 1, then click ok."

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:-1
msgid "046.png"
msgstr "046.png"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:91
msgid "图表 5-9 xrdp登录界面"
msgstr "Figure 5-9 xrdp Login Interface"

#: ../../source/ARTManual/art_ros2.rst:92
msgid "进入ubuntu桌面后可能会多次弹出授权窗口，要求输入密码，此时填入1按回车即可，最后可以正常显示桌面。"
msgstr ""
"After entering the Ubuntu desktop, the authorization window may pop up "
"multiple times, prompting you to enter a password. At this time, enter 1 and"
" press Enter. Finally, the desktop can be displayed normally."

